  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, W-ON-01 trigger)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions at Model Risk Level 5. The intended use is absolute hemolysis-level prediction for a Class III implantable VAD; the clinical decision context is pre-market submission support for a continuous-flow rotary pump operating at 3–6 L/min and 2000–4000 RPM. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors are addressed. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. Despite gaps in several factors, the overall evidence package was accepted under the Minimal profile. NOTE: structured hasContextOfUse link is intentionally absent (W-ON-01 adversarial trigger); use-scope information appears only in this prose field.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou2-hemolysis-vad-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou2-cfd-hemolysis-absolute-prediction",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/morrison-cfd-hemolysis-centrifugal-pump",
